[SN]TITLE[SN]
Luis Alberto: Lazio sign Liverpool forward for £4.3m

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Lazio have signed Liverpool forward Luis Alberto for £4.3m.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Alberto, 23, made 12 appearances for the Reds after he was signed by former manager Brendan Rodgers from Sevilla in a £6.8m deal in June 2013.
He impressed while on loan at Spanish side Deportivo La Coruna last season, scoring six goals in 29 La Liga appearances.
The fee also includes add-ons and a 30% sell-on clause for the Premier League side.
